item.title: cat paw
item.description: 13:59 Tuesday 12 December 2017 JST Giving Jennie some cuddles today, I noticed an extra pad on her foot. Hmmm. That’s not a pad, that’s a swollen something something. fortunately Lin still had time to take her to the clinic; I am headed to work now. Hopefully and presumably she will be okay!

item.title: coughy so went to clinic
item.description: 10:24 Friday 21 July 2017 JST Lin drove me to a clinic today because I got some kinda cold, and have been coughing for a while. Doc said it isn’t contageous, but gave me four (4) different meds to take 3 times a day for 5 days.

item.title: busy skin
item.description: 09:46 Friday 09 December 2016 JST I just went to a dermetologist near our station to ask about a weird pimple thing on my arm, cracks in the callouses on my feet, and itchy face. I was rewarded with a prescription for four types of cream / ointment.
